Title: Nonrelativistic Quantum Particle in a Curved Space as a Constrained  System
Authors: A. Foerster and H. O. Girotti and P. S. Kuhn
Abstract: The operator and the functional formulations of the dynamics of constrained systems are explored for determining unambiguously the quantum Hamiltonian of a nonrelativistic particle in a curved space.
